00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:16,620
 And in fact, when you read the Psalm in Hebrew,

148
00:06:16,620 --> 00:06:18,300
 verse three and four,

149
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:20,820
 verse three speaking about the right paths

150
00:06:20,820 --> 00:06:22,100
 that God leads us on,

151
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:24,500
 and verse four talking about the valley

