00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:35,400
 It's like David wants you to understand

157
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:38,820
 that the right paths and the valleys that are dark

158
00:06:38,820 --> 00:06:42,700
 can sometimes be two realities of the same moment in life.

