 within the Judean hills.

222
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:56,860
 And they were shaped sort of really narrowly.

223
00:09:56,860 --> 00:09:58,180
 Sometimes to get through them,

224
00:09:58,180 --> 00:10:00,980
 you could only get through the rocks single file.

225
00:10:00,980 --> 00:10:04,700
 There were quite high as well, craggy, broken rocks.

226
00:10:04,700 --> 00:10:07,940
 And you would have to go down in through the valley

227
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:10,060
 in order to get out the other side

